            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Marcus [[Opellius]] Antoninus [[Diadumenianus]] most noble Caesar, first among the youth, son of Imperator Caesar Marcus [[Opellius]] Severus [[Macrinus]] Pius Felix Augustus, with tribunician power, consul designate for the 2nd time, father of the fatherland, proconsul. Curated by Valerius Titanianus, prefect of the watchmen, most eminent man, (and) Flavius Lupus, subprefect. </p> 
